Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.52,0:02:42.84,staff,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(289,188)\fad(500,0)}澄空學園
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.94,0:01:35.38,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}在那坡道的中途 你先離開了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.52,0:01:40.95,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}留下了無數珍貴的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.08,0:01:46.23,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我孤單地在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.37,0:01:53.53,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}回味著那些溫馨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.99,0:02:01.63,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}只有你 只有你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.73,0:02:07.60,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}只喜歡著你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.72,0:02:15.50,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}風沙遮眼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.62,0:02:22.52,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}你漸漸遠去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.41,0:02:24.93,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(600,600)\pos(320,348)}無論何時 都還記得
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.53,0:02:26.95,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(600,600)\pos(320,348)}即便一切 天翻地覆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.55,0:02:29.01,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(600,600)\pos(320,348)}唯有那件 唯有那件
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.61,0:02:31.70,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(600,600)\pos(320,348)}日常之事 不曾改變
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.30,0:02:35.91,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(600,600)\pos(320,348)}看一看吧 那充滿光芒的唯一
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.41,0:02:40.72,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(600,600)\pos(320,348)}永遠永遠都在守護著
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.71,0:22:25.93,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}凝望著朵朵流逝的雲彩
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.23,0:22:32.86,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}感受著變化無窮的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.74,0:22:41.07,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}駐足而立的我們察覺到
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.30,0:22:48.26,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}這不斷變遷的世界編織出的歌曲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.35,0:22:55.53,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}彷彿伸出手來追尋一般
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.64,0:23:03.99,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}去尋找那恆久不變的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.48,0:23:11.69,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}手裏高舉著的火炬
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.84,0:23:19.50,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}是通向明天的小小路標
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.50,0:23:26.74,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}現在依然明亮
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.02,0:23:34.37,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}那一天的言語化為誓約
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.48,0:23:39.22,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}激勵我們前進
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.16,0:03:18.78,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(322,245)}世界的終結
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.70,0:24:09.70,notice,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,0)\an5\pos(320,245)}小小的手心
