Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.47,0:00:16.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一樣的呢 跟渚小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.09,0:00:22.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遺憾 無法查明原因
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.35,0:00:27.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 估計會像渚小姐一樣今後也一直…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.47,0:00:30.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到剛才為止…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.54,0:00:33.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都還那麼健康的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.19,0:00:42.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我就先告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.41,0:00:58.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋也
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.13,0:01:02.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙的父親是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.88,0:01:04.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.18,0:01:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你就要拿出個做父親的樣子來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.30,0:02:52.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧 你不冷嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.62,0:02:56.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為人偶的我感覺不到寒冷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.34,0:03:00.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但她的手一定變得很冷了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.21,0:03:04.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我連這一點也感覺不到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.51,0:03:10.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快世界就要變得一片雪白了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.29,0:03:13.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得趕快了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.47,0:03:29.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,運動會？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.18,0:03:30.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.43,0:03:35.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸不跑嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.10,0:03:38.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我會一直在你身邊哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.37,0:03:40.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿秋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.64,0:03:42.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔或許會跑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.76,0:03:44.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個最後一棒都休息的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.46,0:03:46.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估計很難能找到人代替的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.21,0:03:52.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 要戰勝阿秋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.48,0:03:56.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要待在你身邊啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.81,0:03:58.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.65,0:04:00.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是站在我這邊的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.37,0:04:02.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.56,0:04:06.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是站在你這邊的 不管發生什麼都會保護你的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.65,0:04:09.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.36,0:04:14.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,困了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.17,0:04:14.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.68,0:04:18.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心 我哪兒也不會去的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.57,0:04:19.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.48,0:04:26.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一星期 兩星期
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.51,0:04:29.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後一個月過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.65,0:04:31.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐的燒仍然沒有退
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.51,0:04:36.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要說是去幼兒園 就連房門都出不了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.56,0:04:38.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.66,0:04:44.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為我來講 實在不想讓岡崎君就這麼辭職了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.66,0:04:47.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過看來你也有很多苦衷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.33,0:04:57.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很果斷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.05,0:05:06.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早苗阿姨跟大叔勸過我 但我想待在汐身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.47,0:05:08.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有積蓄嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.94,0:05:12.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一點 因為有在存她的學費
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.59,0:05:13.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.76,0:05:16.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦你了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.74,0:05:19.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直以來非常感謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.76,0:05:28.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶上吧 別弄丟了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.60,0:05:31.52,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}手柄上刻的是「芳野」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.40,0:05:33.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.81,0:05:37.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能 明天開始的工作會很困擾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.77,0:05:38.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.98,0:05:43.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為交換把你的螺絲刀借給我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.93,0:05:45.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等你回來了就還給你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.87,0:05:51.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等小汐好點了就回來吧 在那之前就借我用用
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.75,0:06:15.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會愛惜的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.52,0:06:23.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐一直在家裏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.04,0:06:26.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有考慮過住院 但最後還是沒有去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.61,0:06:32.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有治療方法的話 就算去了也沒有多大意義
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.02,0:06:36.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更重要的是 汐想要待在家裏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.97,0:06:39.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡衣換一套新的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.51,0:06:40.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.33,0:06:46.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用起來哦 爸爸會幫你換的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.33,0:06:48.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一個人能行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.96,0:07:03.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用勉強 現在就算一個人做不到也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.72,0:07:05.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.37,0:07:08.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐已經不能一個人換衣服了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.60,0:07:10.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不能一個人上廁所了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.45,0:07:13.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飯也只能吃些不太硬的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.66,0:07:19.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平穩的日常生活 是不是不會再回來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.32,0:07:30.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐 有想要的東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.55,0:07:35.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有的話就說哦 不論是玩具還是吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.38,0:07:37.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是什麼我都會給你買的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.31,0:07:42.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想去旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.38,0:07:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅行？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.42,0:07:46.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還想跟爸爸一起去旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.84,0:07:50.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種事一點也不開心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.47,0:07:53.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸脾氣不好 還會大聲吼叫什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.23,0:07:57.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很開心 還想去旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.89,0:08:02.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乘上電車 跟爸爸一起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.99,0:08:05.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等你病好了就去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.56,0:08:08.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就想去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.80,0:08:14.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐 不要為難爸爸好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.20,0:08:15.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.30,0:08:21.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己女兒的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.86,0:08:25.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一的一個願望 我也不能幫她實現嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.65,0:08:27.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.14,0:08:29.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底怎麼辦才好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.03,0:08:32.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個時候如果有你在的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.68,0:08:38.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.19,0:08:40.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一家人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.91,0:08:43.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是單純地被這個小鎮所玩弄著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.38,0:08:46.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輕易地被賦予了幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.70,0:08:48.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後又被輕易地奪去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.16,0:08:52.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.37,0:08:56.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要救汐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.26,0:08:58.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.29,0:09:03.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.39,0:09:05.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.32,0:09:06.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.29,0:09:14.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.26,0:09:20.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能收啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.96,0:09:22.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這麼固執
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.76,0:09:25.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我並不是固執
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.51,0:09:28.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還有點積蓄 還能撐一陣子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.68,0:09:30.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要敢騙我的話就修理你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.69,0:09:31.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.32,0:09:34.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.72,0:09:38.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人難做
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.11,0:09:40.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但該守護的東西還是必須守護好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.02,0:09:41.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.71,0:09:46.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 真到不行的時候會跟你說的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.42,0:10:12.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.29,0:10:15.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我戒掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.40,0:10:17.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是明智的選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.61,0:10:21.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.26,0:10:27.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人們犧牲了這片大自然建起了這所醫院
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.16,0:10:31.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來會犧牲什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.18,0:10:37.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鎮外的山丘已經開始被挖開了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.76,0:10:40.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎要建個購物街
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.75,0:10:44.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為會變得方便 所以對居民來說是件好事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.08,0:10:47.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會不會是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.40,0:10:52.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從你把快要不行了的渚帶到這裏來的時候開始
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.61,0:10:55.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚就和這座小鎮連接在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.93,0:10:58.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後渚的女兒汐也
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.80,0:11:03.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漸漸被改變
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.58,0:11:05.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漸漸被改變樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.10,0:11:08.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對這座小鎮來說是痛苦嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.18,0:11:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這和痛苦沒什麼關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.55,0:11:18.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「啊 漸漸地在改變」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.48,0:11:21.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鎮只會這樣覺得吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.52,0:11:27.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果人的死也只是被改變的一步
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.93,0:11:30.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們就不得不接受這個事實嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.64,0:11:35.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因為人們不願接受 才建起了醫院
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.47,0:11:56.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,願這座小鎮和居民們 幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.20,0:12:47.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,口渴了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.18,0:12:49.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要喝水嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.34,0:13:02.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很涼 要慢慢喝哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.72,0:13:05.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一口氣喝下去會鬧肚子的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.01,0:13:15.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.63,0:13:16.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.76,0:13:17.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.87,0:13:24.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想去旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.01,0:13:27.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 等你病好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.04,0:13:29.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想去哪裏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.53,0:13:32.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還去那片花田嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.94,0:13:35.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是現在去北方的話會很冷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.88,0:13:36.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去南方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.45,0:13:41.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既溫暖又熱鬧的 空氣新鮮的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.42,0:13:42.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說去…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.17,0:13:43.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在就想去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.96,0:13:48.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要等你病好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.38,0:13:49.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說了好幾次了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.70,0:13:53.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在 現在就想去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.35,0:13:54.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去那片花田
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.38,0:13:56.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.52,0:13:59.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要現在才行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.96,0:14:03.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想和爸爸兩人一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.15,0:14:16.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.46,0:14:19.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就聽你的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.27,0:14:20.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.88,0:14:25.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是如果不舒服了就要老老實實地告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.30,0:14:26.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.41,0:14:28.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.69,0:14:34.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我背你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.68,0:14:36.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.12,0:14:39.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要一個人走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.63,0:14:41.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說了不要勉強的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.56,0:14:45.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想和爸爸一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.63,0:14:46.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.94,0:14:49.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就一起走到你能走到的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.21,0:14:50.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.70,0:14:52.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.09,0:14:55.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次就快快樂樂地旅行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.46,0:14:57.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.29,0:15:12.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧 汐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.03,0:15:13.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.11,0:15:17.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真的不舒服的話一定要告訴我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.99,0:15:19.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我帶你去看醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.10,0:15:20.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.44,0:15:46.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐 已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.34,0:16:02.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是雪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.53,0:16:18.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐喜歡雪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.11,0:16:19.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.07,0:16:22.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸也喜歡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.38,0:16:24.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.14,0:16:29.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 爸爸也很喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.43,0:16:32.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還能走嗎 汐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.14,0:16:34.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要稍微休息一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.78,0:16:35.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.50,0:16:38.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁還沒有下大前上車吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.39,0:16:40.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來背你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.18,0:16:41.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.97,0:17:34.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.48,0:17:50.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.68,0:17:52.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 汐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.24,0:17:55.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在…在哪裏？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.66,0:17:57.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在電車裏了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.15,0:18:01.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 已經在電車裏了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.07,0:18:05.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好黑 已經是晚上了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.29,0:18:08.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 已經是深夜了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.00,0:18:10.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.09,0:18:13.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.43,0:18:15.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最喜歡了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.98,0:18:16.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.70,0:18:21.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸也最喜歡汐了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.06,0:18:34.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.07,0:18:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.67,0:18:42.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.16,0:19:01.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.70,0:19:02.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.72,0:19:04.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.09,0:19:07.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救汐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.42,0:19:11.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.14,0:19:17.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰來 誰來救救汐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.71,0:19:20.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.03,0:19:57.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.83,0:20:14.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要走多久才能到達呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.39,0:20:18.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是已經近在眼前了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.33,0:20:24.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說 仍舊遙不可及呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.31,0:20:54.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我討厭這座小鎮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.23,0:21:01.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這裏充滿了想要忘卻的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.22,0:21:08.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天去學校聽聽課 和朋友聊聊天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.09,0:21:11.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到根本不想回去的家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.57,0:21:16.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去 以後會有什麼改變嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.20,0:21:20.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不一樣的生活會到來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.21,0:21:32.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.49,0:21:33.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豆沙麵包
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.47,0:21:37.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡這所學校嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.70,0:21:43.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我非常非常喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.53,0:21:44.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 所有的這一切
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.99,0:21:47.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都在不斷改變著
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.12,0:21:52.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裏和她搭話的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.00,0:21:55.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就會和渚相遇 開始交往
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.80,0:21:57.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.20,0:22:00.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是不這樣做比較好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.40,0:22:03.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有這次的邂逅…

